WEBVTT

00:00:10.600 --> 00:00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

00:01:06.540 --> 00:01:08.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

00:01:12.020 --> 00:01:15.140
[Episode 33]

00:01:29.240 --> 00:01:30.250
Uncle, save me!

00:01:32.470 --> 00:01:32.890
Let's go.

00:01:34.160 --> 00:01:34.650
Out of the way!

00:01:40.440 --> 00:01:40.980
Uncle.

00:01:41.270 --> 00:01:42.220
Miaoqing is hurt!

00:02:33.390 --> 00:02:34.300
The child is gone.

00:02:35.270 --> 00:02:35.970
Get some rest.

00:02:52.040 --> 00:02:52.650
Take a sip.

00:03:05.990 --> 00:03:06.530
Drink it.

00:03:19.590 --> 00:03:20.810
I hate you.

00:03:23.240 --> 00:03:24.570
I hate you.

00:03:55.150 --> 00:03:56.500
I hate you!

00:04:33.030 --> 00:04:34.060
Immortal Lord Xuanhua,

00:04:35.080 --> 00:04:36.420
Why such a grand display?

00:04:37.270 --> 00:04:38.500
What brings you here?

00:04:51.470 --> 00:04:52.300
Mr. Zuo Qiu,

00:04:53.390 --> 00:04:55.420
I respect the academy as a pillar of the immortal sects,

00:04:56.080 --> 00:04:56.940
Always staying out of conflict.

00:04:57.680 --> 00:04:59.620
But now you're harboring the Demon Lord and the Divine Tree.

00:05:00.230 --> 00:05:01.100
What are you trying to do?

00:05:02.080 --> 00:05:03.570
Are you betraying the immortal sects

00:05:04.390 --> 00:05:05.370
To side with those across the sea?

00:05:06.080 --> 00:05:09.250
The academy has only masters and disciples.

00:05:09.960 --> 00:05:11.740
No Demon Lord or Divine Tree.

00:05:13.520 --> 00:05:15.500
A few days ago, an assassin came after me,

00:05:16.760 --> 00:05:18.890
But was rescued by the Demon Lord Yecha and the Divine Tree.

00:05:19.270 --> 00:05:21.250
That assassin was struck by my fire lotus spell.

00:05:21.830 --> 00:05:23.210
With a little push...

00:05:40.230 --> 00:05:40.770
Look.

00:05:41.760 --> 00:05:43.810
The assassin, Baili Gelin, is at the academy.

00:05:44.910 --> 00:05:47.620
The Divine Tree and the Demon Lord are here too.

00:05:49.830 --> 00:05:50.570
Ji Tongzhou,

00:05:52.030 --> 00:05:53.570
You killed Changyue and Ye!

00:05:54.270 --> 00:05:55.660
As long as I draw breath,

00:05:56.230 --> 00:05:57.540
I will kill you for revenge!

00:05:58.270 --> 00:05:58.810
Don't move.

00:05:58.830 --> 00:06:00.060
I'll say it once more.

00:06:00.590 --> 00:06:02.890
The academy has only masters and disciples.

00:06:03.590 --> 00:06:05.130
No Demon Lord, Divine Tree,

00:06:05.830 --> 00:06:06.890
Or assassin.

00:06:07.270 --> 00:06:08.940
Since you insist,

00:06:09.710 --> 00:06:11.370
Don't blame me for being rude.

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:12.500
Search.

00:06:12.520 --> 00:06:13.130
Yes.

00:06:13.320 --> 00:06:13.940
Don't you dare!

00:06:23.790 --> 00:06:24.620
Immortal Lord Xuanhua,

00:06:25.270 --> 00:06:26.940
Chufeng Academy is a sacred ground of the immortal sects.

00:06:27.270 --> 00:06:29.060
They've always stayed out of disputes.

00:06:29.880 --> 00:06:32.420
You brazenly disrupt the peace of the academy.

00:06:32.910 --> 00:06:34.210
Aren't you afraid of public outrage?

00:06:45.790 --> 00:06:46.420
Fine.

00:06:47.880 --> 00:06:49.690
Out of respect for the academy's teachings,

00:06:51.000 --> 00:06:52.330
I'll give you one day.

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:54.890
Hand over the Demon Lord and the Divine Tree by tomorrow morning.

00:06:55.470 --> 00:06:56.100
Otherwise,

00:06:57.680 --> 00:06:59.370
I'll burn Chufeng Academy to the ground

00:07:03.910 --> 00:07:05.180
And smoke them out.

00:07:48.590 --> 00:07:49.890
I knew you two were still alive.

00:07:51.030 --> 00:07:52.300
All these years, every divination I made

00:07:52.590 --> 00:07:54.130
Pointed to a reunion with old friends.

00:07:56.680 --> 00:07:57.620
Do you two

00:07:57.960 --> 00:07:58.690
Have any conscience at all?

00:07:59.200 --> 00:07:59.890
You're fine,

00:07:59.910 --> 00:08:01.890
And you didn't even send word?

00:08:02.120 --> 00:08:02.890
Deng,

00:08:04.150 --> 00:08:05.690
You're a Sect Leader now.

00:08:05.910 --> 00:08:07.300
Can you at least act like one?

00:08:10.080 --> 00:08:10.740
You left

00:08:11.880 --> 00:08:13.130
For ten whole years.

00:08:13.760 --> 00:08:15.450
Do you know how worried your master was?

00:08:16.390 --> 00:08:17.420
How is

00:08:18.080 --> 00:08:18.810
My master?

00:08:20.710 --> 00:08:22.690
His cultivation has dropped sharply.

00:08:23.270 --> 00:08:24.940
He's retired to Hushe Peak now.

00:08:27.390 --> 00:08:29.250
But he's quite carefree these days.

00:08:29.910 --> 00:08:31.210
He often discusses medicine and the Dao

00:08:31.230 --> 00:08:32.980
With Elder Dongyang and Elder Zhu.

00:08:35.560 --> 00:08:36.940
I almost forgot the main thing.

00:08:40.440 --> 00:08:41.420
Elder Dongyang asked me

00:08:41.440 --> 00:08:42.780
To bring you this miraculous pill.

00:08:43.400 --> 00:08:44.780
He said your cultivation has declined.

00:08:44.920 --> 00:08:45.730
Take this,

00:08:45.870 --> 00:08:47.060
And it'll secure your future well-being.

00:08:48.710 --> 00:08:50.210
They're always so thoughtful.

00:08:50.800 --> 00:08:52.490
Xiuyuan and I could really use some medicine right now.

00:08:55.350 --> 00:08:56.300
Only one pill?

00:08:58.750 --> 00:08:59.450
What do you mean?

00:09:00.280 --> 00:09:02.180
Your master traveled far and wide,

00:09:02.200 --> 00:09:02.970
Searching for the finest herbs,

00:09:02.990 --> 00:09:03.970
Just to refine this single pill.

00:09:09.800 --> 00:09:10.540
You've just been hurt.

00:09:11.280 --> 00:09:11.850
Take it.

00:09:28.200 --> 00:09:28.940
I still have my spirit root.

00:09:29.230 --> 00:09:29.780
I can recultivate.

00:09:29.960 --> 00:09:30.420
You...

00:09:39.510 --> 00:09:40.570
My spirit power is back?

00:09:43.510 --> 00:09:45.420
The pill only strengthens the body and prolongs life.

00:09:45.960 --> 00:09:49.060
Your spirit power must have returned because of the medicine.

00:09:49.470 --> 00:09:50.180
It only works once.

00:09:52.750 --> 00:09:54.490
It doesn't matter. It's still a gain.

00:09:56.680 --> 00:09:57.090
By the way,

00:09:57.630 --> 00:09:59.490
Ji Tongzhou gave the academy a one-day ultimatum.

00:10:00.470 --> 00:10:01.140
What do you two think?

00:10:07.960 --> 00:10:09.180
Fight him to the death!

00:10:14.750 --> 00:10:15.300
Gelin,

00:10:15.870 --> 00:10:17.090
You were imprisoned and wounded.

00:10:17.110 --> 00:10:17.900
Your spirit power is weak.

00:10:18.280 --> 00:10:19.140
You should return to the East Sea.

00:10:19.830 --> 00:10:20.940
No, I don't want to run away.

00:10:22.630 --> 00:10:24.060
If I don't avenge Changyue and Ye,

00:10:24.510 --> 00:10:25.850
I'll never have peace.

00:10:27.470 --> 00:10:28.380
Even if it costs me my life,

00:10:29.470 --> 00:10:30.660
I'll fight him to the end.

00:10:32.080 --> 00:10:34.020
Ji Tongzhou has been crushing his opponents for these years.

00:10:34.830 --> 00:10:35.940
He's made plenty of enemies.

00:10:36.870 --> 00:10:39.090
Lately, Xingzheng Hall has wiped out several immortal sects.

00:10:39.560 --> 00:10:41.260
Wuyue Court also wants to curb his ambitions.

00:10:41.680 --> 00:10:42.570
This is our chance.

00:10:43.680 --> 00:10:45.090
But what exactly is

00:10:45.470 --> 00:10:46.490
The karmic fire?

00:10:47.280 --> 00:10:49.060
Karmic fire comes from the inner demon.

00:10:50.160 --> 00:10:51.730
Mr. Zuo Qiu found the Xuanhua Sacred Fire Record

00:10:51.750 --> 00:10:52.780
In Futu Tower.

00:10:53.350 --> 00:10:54.060
It says

00:10:54.470 --> 00:10:55.380
Those who wield karmic fire

00:10:55.800 --> 00:10:57.060
Are usually people with deep obsessions,

00:10:57.470 --> 00:10:58.450
Driven to the brink of despair.

00:10:58.800 --> 00:10:59.260
The fire

00:10:59.350 --> 00:11:01.090
Is their only weapon of retaliation.

00:11:01.590 --> 00:11:03.690
That's why it's also called the fire of the inner demon.

00:11:06.400 --> 00:11:07.450
Inner demon?

00:11:08.800 --> 00:11:09.660
Inner demon?

00:11:11.110 --> 00:11:13.260
Is this the aftermath of the mirage dream

00:11:13.630 --> 00:11:14.570
On Fanghu Island?

00:11:17.200 --> 00:11:18.730
Karmic fire is born from the inner demon.

00:11:19.710 --> 00:11:21.330
So if we get rid of the inner demon,

00:11:21.960 --> 00:11:23.690
The fire will die out?

00:11:24.830 --> 00:11:25.780
Not that easy.

00:11:26.230 --> 00:11:27.380
To get rid of the inner demon,

00:11:27.830 --> 00:11:29.140
You must first understand the obsession.

00:11:32.560 --> 00:11:33.610
I know what his obsession is.

00:11:35.040 --> 00:11:36.210
But even knowing it,

00:11:36.560 --> 00:11:38.810
We'd have to push him to the edge before we could act.

00:11:39.470 --> 00:11:40.490
And who in this world

00:11:41.110 --> 00:11:43.090
Can push Immortal Lord Xuanhua to the edge?

00:11:50.830 --> 00:11:51.490
Let me try.

00:11:53.990 --> 00:11:55.330
Mr. Zuo already knew you'd say that.

00:11:56.200 --> 00:11:56.690
Follow me.

00:12:03.630 --> 00:12:04.900
Human strength has its limits.

00:12:05.470 --> 00:12:06.380
In just one day,

00:12:06.630 --> 00:12:08.810
How can Xiuyuan stand against Immortal Lord Xuanhua?

00:12:12.400 --> 00:12:13.690
One person's strength is limited.

00:12:15.230 --> 00:12:17.850
But when generations share the same will,

00:12:18.510 --> 00:12:20.090
Spanning centuries without end,

00:12:21.160 --> 00:12:22.660
It becomes limitless.

00:12:24.680 --> 00:12:25.300
Sir.

00:12:44.560 --> 00:12:45.940
You only have one chance.

00:12:46.510 --> 00:12:47.690
Hold Ji Tongzhou back.

00:12:48.280 --> 00:12:50.210
Help Lifei turn the tide!

00:13:07.320 --> 00:13:08.940
Mr. Zuo, you gave him the academy's spirit energy.

00:13:10.040 --> 00:13:10.850
Thousands of years ago,

00:13:11.510 --> 00:13:12.940
I founded Chufeng Academy.

00:13:13.350 --> 00:13:16.780
It was meant to be a place beyond the affairs of this world.

00:13:17.510 --> 00:13:19.450
Yet all things in this world are connected.

00:13:20.110 --> 00:13:21.660
Nothing is truly detached.

00:13:22.320 --> 00:13:25.490
My spirit root was destroyed long ago.

00:13:25.960 --> 00:13:28.380
I've only survived on the academy's spirit energy.

00:13:28.750 --> 00:13:29.330
Now

00:13:29.710 --> 00:13:31.210
It's up to the younger generation.

00:13:31.920 --> 00:13:33.810
Mr. Zuo, you sacrificed your cultivation

00:13:34.230 --> 00:13:35.330
To build the mountain-sea barrier,

00:13:35.800 --> 00:13:36.900
Protecting the Central Plains

00:13:37.630 --> 00:13:38.940
And preserving the flame of the immortal sects.

00:13:39.590 --> 00:13:44.020
From now on, it's these flames that will carry on.

00:13:52.510 --> 00:13:52.780
Mr...

00:13:55.870 --> 00:13:56.420
Mr. Zuo.

00:14:01.830 --> 00:14:03.570
With growth comes decay.

00:14:05.320 --> 00:14:06.610
Let nature take its course.

00:14:08.560 --> 00:14:09.780
Don't dwell on it.

00:14:48.230 --> 00:14:50.090
We don't know if we'll survive tomorrow's battle.

00:14:53.280 --> 00:14:55.780
I'm dragging you into this again.

00:14:57.350 --> 00:14:58.020
Silly.

00:14:59.230 --> 00:15:00.140
We're husband and wife.

00:15:00.990 --> 00:15:02.140
We live and die together.

00:15:18.590 --> 00:15:19.570
I want to stay at the academy.

00:15:21.040 --> 00:15:21.540
Why?

00:15:24.870 --> 00:15:27.690
When I was young, I relied on Changyue and Ye.

00:15:28.990 --> 00:15:29.850
In the East Sea,

00:15:30.750 --> 00:15:32.260
I had Jiao and you.

00:15:33.990 --> 00:15:36.090
I always hesitated before doing anything.

00:15:36.870 --> 00:15:38.020
My cultivation was average.

00:15:38.710 --> 00:15:39.420
I never knew

00:15:39.440 --> 00:15:40.900
What I truly wanted.

00:15:41.750 --> 00:15:42.540
But today,

00:15:44.510 --> 00:15:45.210
Watching the masters

00:15:45.230 --> 00:15:46.780
Stand up to Ji Tongzhou,

00:15:47.470 --> 00:15:48.420
I finally understood.

00:15:49.590 --> 00:15:50.780
Even dust may fight the storm.

00:15:51.560 --> 00:15:53.420
We ordinary people have our own reason for being.

00:15:55.080 --> 00:15:56.060
So I want to stay.

00:15:57.440 --> 00:15:59.300
I want to show my future juniors

00:16:00.470 --> 00:16:01.810
What it means that all beings are equal,

00:16:03.160 --> 00:16:04.660
To fear no power,

00:16:05.230 --> 00:16:06.380
To hold a sense of justice,

00:16:07.590 --> 00:16:08.540
And to walk the Great Dao.

00:16:09.830 --> 00:16:10.210
Alright.

00:16:13.470 --> 00:16:14.210
Then we'll

00:16:14.960 --> 00:16:15.970
Seek the Great Dao together.

00:17:11.360 --> 00:17:12.450
You're finally here.

00:17:17.880 --> 00:17:18.660
Come at me together.

00:17:19.710 --> 00:17:21.180
Save me the trouble.

00:18:04.790 --> 00:18:05.250
Form the formation!

00:18:16.160 --> 00:18:17.730
Demon-Subduing Formation?

00:18:19.840 --> 00:18:21.660
You dare use that against me?

00:18:22.680 --> 00:18:23.580
Ridiculous.

00:20:39.230 --> 00:20:41.380
Fire and metal unite. The karmic fire is merciless.

00:20:41.990 --> 00:20:42.900
Your own karmic fire.

00:20:43.470 --> 00:20:43.970
Take it back!

00:21:00.120 --> 00:21:01.100
This is the academy's spirit energy?

00:21:01.840 --> 00:21:02.620
You are the Demon Lord.

00:21:02.920 --> 00:21:03.940
Why are they helping you?

00:21:04.400 --> 00:21:05.140
Spirit power knows no divide.

00:21:06.030 --> 00:21:07.010
Good and evil dwell in the heart!

00:21:23.400 --> 00:21:23.970
Tongzhou,

00:21:24.680 --> 00:21:25.620
You're at your end.

00:21:26.470 --> 00:21:27.290
Time to turn back.

00:22:07.070 --> 00:22:07.660
Tongzhou.

00:22:10.440 --> 00:22:12.340
Tongzhou, why are you asleep?

00:22:17.550 --> 00:22:18.180
Lanya?

00:22:20.070 --> 00:22:22.490
What... what are you doing here?

00:22:27.960 --> 00:22:28.900
What's wrong, Tongzhou?

00:22:29.750 --> 00:22:30.690
Do you hate me?

00:22:30.990 --> 00:22:32.180
Not happy to see me?

00:22:34.470 --> 00:22:36.250
I.. I am happy.

00:23:02.440 --> 00:23:03.010
Tongzhou,

00:23:03.840 --> 00:23:04.490
What's wrong?

00:23:04.920 --> 00:23:06.050
Did you not sleep well last night?

00:23:06.920 --> 00:23:07.770
Ye Ye?

00:23:09.400 --> 00:23:10.620
Ye Ye, you're alive?

00:23:13.030 --> 00:23:15.100
What are you talking about?

00:23:24.030 --> 00:23:24.620
Your Highness,

00:23:25.200 --> 00:23:26.180
You're still half asleep?

00:23:36.440 --> 00:23:37.450
Tongzhou, Mr. Hu is here.

00:23:37.640 --> 00:23:38.100
Sit down.

00:23:41.030 --> 00:23:42.450
Class is about to start.

00:23:42.960 --> 00:23:43.900
Do you all

00:23:44.840 --> 00:23:46.050
Want to be punished?

00:23:51.070 --> 00:23:51.900
Ji Tongzhou!

00:23:53.230 --> 00:23:53.900
Dazing off?

00:23:55.440 --> 00:23:56.380
Still sleepy?

00:23:57.920 --> 00:23:58.820
Were you dreaming?

00:24:01.310 --> 00:24:01.900
A dream?

00:24:04.960 --> 00:24:05.730
Just a dream.

00:24:17.840 --> 00:24:18.770
It really was just a dream.

00:24:34.400 --> 00:24:34.970
Lifei.

00:24:37.840 --> 00:24:38.380
Lifei.

00:24:39.070 --> 00:24:39.690
Xiuyuan!

00:25:11.120 --> 00:25:12.620
Lifei! Xiuyuan!

00:25:15.070 --> 00:25:15.490
Lifei.

00:25:16.230 --> 00:25:17.770
I just had the longest dream.

00:25:18.440 --> 00:25:19.010
What did you dream about?

00:25:19.160 --> 00:25:19.730
I dreamed...

00:25:21.920 --> 00:25:23.860
Forget it. Don't tell dreams in broad daylight.

00:25:24.470 --> 00:25:25.940
My brother brought lots of food.

00:25:26.120 --> 00:25:27.100
Everyone will love it.

00:25:27.920 --> 00:25:29.140
Xiuyuan, join us.

00:25:30.360 --> 00:25:30.860
Let's go.

00:25:49.230 --> 00:25:50.100
Need to knead it more.

00:25:50.510 --> 00:25:51.730
- Changyue. - Like this.

00:25:52.790 --> 00:25:53.900
I got it, Changyue.

00:25:54.120 --> 00:25:54.900
You're doing so well.

00:25:56.200 --> 00:25:57.100
Almost done. See?

00:25:57.550 --> 00:25:58.010
Tongzhou,

00:25:58.880 --> 00:25:59.770
Come make mooncakes with us.

00:26:05.680 --> 00:26:06.180
Done.

00:26:06.400 --> 00:26:07.380
Drink till we drop!

00:26:07.920 --> 00:26:08.490
Drink till we drop.

00:26:09.640 --> 00:26:10.180
Here.

00:26:13.400 --> 00:26:14.420
Come on.

00:26:16.880 --> 00:26:18.490
Let's release this wish lantern together.

00:26:19.030 --> 00:26:19.530
Sure.

00:26:19.990 --> 00:26:22.010
But what should we write?

00:26:29.120 --> 00:26:30.100
"May we be together forever."

00:26:30.920 --> 00:26:31.900
"The same every year."

00:26:32.600 --> 00:26:33.660
"May we be together forever."

00:26:34.750 --> 00:26:35.820
"The same every year."

00:26:37.230 --> 00:26:37.770
Alright.

00:26:55.440 --> 00:26:56.960
[May we be together forever. The same every year.]

00:27:02.160 --> 00:27:04.340
If only time could stop right here.

00:27:05.440 --> 00:27:06.380
Right, Tongzhou?

00:27:31.550 --> 00:27:32.050
Don't go!

00:27:47.790 --> 00:27:48.900
Immortal Lord Xuanhua?

00:27:53.160 --> 00:27:53.530
That...

00:28:00.270 --> 00:28:01.140
That's me?

00:28:15.640 --> 00:28:16.180
Tongzhou.

00:28:17.550 --> 00:28:18.210
Time to wake up.

00:28:26.030 --> 00:28:28.210
Tongzhou, we never blamed you.

00:28:35.030 --> 00:28:35.730
Sorry.

00:28:40.360 --> 00:28:40.970
I'm sorry.

00:28:55.710 --> 00:28:56.940
Why don't you blame me?

00:29:00.030 --> 00:29:01.770
I did so many wrong things.

00:29:11.400 --> 00:29:12.820
Why don't you blame me?

00:29:47.510 --> 00:29:49.900
A dream. Just a dream.

00:29:50.680 --> 00:29:52.100
All of this was a dream!

00:30:17.750 --> 00:30:18.490
What's happening?

00:30:20.710 --> 00:30:21.530
His mind is broken.

00:30:22.550 --> 00:30:23.620
He can't use Xuanhua Fire anymore.

00:30:31.550 --> 00:30:33.180
Ji Tongzhou, pay with your life!

00:30:57.990 --> 00:30:58.420
No.

00:31:11.400 --> 00:31:11.970
Miaoqing.

00:31:12.920 --> 00:31:13.530
Miaoqing.

00:31:14.040 --> 00:31:17.310
♪The warmth within my arms♪

00:31:17.310 --> 00:31:17.940
Miaoqing!

00:31:18.110 --> 00:31:21.150
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

00:31:21.450 --> 00:31:24.850
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

